Yes, it is still an issue. But I manually copy MakeCheckOpValueString function from logging.cc
and it works.

namespace tensorflow {
   namespace internal {
   	template <>
   	void MakeCheckOpValueString(std::ostream* os, const unsigned char& v) {
   		if (v >= 32 && v <= 126) {
   			(*os) << "'" << v << "'";
   		}
   		else {
   			(*os) << "unsigned char value " << static_cast<unsigned short>(v);
   		}
   	}
   }
}
